itunes:title: Are you an OVER GIVER? talking Boundaries Attachments EXPECTATIONS and Guilt | EP 47
title: Are you an OVER GIVER? talking Boundaries Attachments EXPECTATIONS and Guilt | EP 47
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description:
Over giving…. we are all guilty of it at one time or another! So do we stop giving to those who just seem to take from us? Or do we keep on giving because that’s who we are?


Too many women feel like they are constantly giving to others and not receiving the same in return, and we’ve probably been on the other side of that spectrum as well (if we are being honest). Are you an over giver or a taker? What would you do if you felt your generosity was being taken advantage of?!


We are also on Spotify, Apple Podcast and more! Search "Yeah No I Know".

* Everything we talk about on this podcast is our own individual opinions, not fact. Research everything for yourself and make the best decisions for you.
